OL,5, A sex education theatre show aimed at  
OL,6, children has been cancelled after the  
OL,7, venue said it had received             
OL,8, "unprecedented threats and abuse".     
OL,10,FThe Family Sex Show, featuring topics  
OL,11,Fsuch as consent, pleasure and          
OL,12,Fqueerness, was due to be performed at  
OL,13,FBristol's Tobacco Factory in May.      
OL,15,FThe creators of the show, who said they
OL,16,Fhad also received threats, have now    
OL,17,Fcancelled its whole tour.              
OL,19,FMore than 38,000 people signed a       
OL,20,Fpetition calling for it to be axed.    
